                  type="person">Kraus</rs> – <rs ref="https://pmb.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/entity/36922"
                  type="institution">Augsburger Stadt<lb break="no"
                     xml:id="uuid_3587406e-990f-4b72-8a8a-c31cab8b8730"/>theater</rs><lb
                  xml:id="uuid_55d8cebf-2df3-4431-acab-d1c1ac9669fd"/>exp. 26.6.1930.</note>
         </p>
